[node name="Menu UI" type="Control" parent="." unique_id=1619821471]
process_mode = 3
visible = false
layout_mode = 3
anchors_preset = 15
anchor_right = 1.0
anchor_bottom = 1.0
grow_horizontal = 2
grow_vertical = 2
script = ExtResource("9_yv0d0")
options = Array[String](["Toggle build mode: B
Toggle driving: V
Cycle selected part: E and Q
Move part place position: W, A, S, and D
Place part: F
Remove Part: Y
Set part parent: U
Reset part parent: N
Change servo group: G and H
Pickup trash: Y
Rotate part: All arrows + Comma + Dot
Toggle Magnet: R
Activate propeller: Space
Rotate servo: [ and ]
Rotate elevator servo: w and s
Rotate aileron servo: a and d
Swap driving direction: P
Swap steering Direction: L", "To build a vehicle, start with a frame(a good first frame would be 3 blocks long and 1 block wide). Then find the wheel(steer) part and place 1 on each side of the front of your vehicle, you may need to rotate the wheels so they face the right way. Do the same for the back but with normal wheels. Finally add some power(start with solar panels) until you have at least 0 net power. If you want to, you can add a seat so specify the camera location and also I would recommend adding some blocks at the front of your vehicle to help your pickup some trash.", "To drive your car, exit build mode a press the toggle driving button. Use the movment keys to drive around, then try to find some of the trash you require. Use whatever you have to pickup some trash and drive it back to the recyling centre. You will be given an option of what you want to make it into.", "Funtional Trash:
Appearance: A jumble of multiple colors in the rough shape of a cube.
Uses: All of the functional block including mechanical(eg servo) and power but not including wheels and seats.
Frame Trash:
Appeance: A white and orange with lots of cube shapes
Uses: Used to make basic blocks and slopes
Vehicle Trash:
Appearance: Black tires with orange on them
Uses: Used to makes wheels and seats
One more thing: if you take enough trash from one area it will clear it of trash and the area will grow back", "Block: A basic cube shaped block
Wheel: A motorised wheel that dosent turn
Wheel(steer): A motorised wheel that turns
Servo: A part that can rotate other parts attahed to it when the current part is set to it
Seat: A part that sets where the camera centers when driving and sets where the player is when driving
Slopes: Slope shaped parts
Magnet: A part that can hold 1 trash when enabled
Generators: Generates power to be able to drive
Wing: Can be used to generate lift
Propeller: Generates thrust
Flap Servos: Like a servo but faster, resets, and has controlls for a plane
Stabilizer: A component of a plane that will stabilize the horizontal movment"])

